Answer: software utility "cron"
		Cron is most suitable for scheduling repetitive tasks.
		Files crontab for individual users situated in /usr/spool/cron/crontabs/
		or /var/spool/cron/tabs/.
		Files crontab using for whole system situated in /etc/cron.d/
		In derictories /etc/cron.daily/, /etc/cron.weekly/ Ð¸ /etc/cron.monthly/
		situated automaticlly run programs (daily, wweek and monthly)
